    "steam_appid": 3077520,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": true,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3077520/extras/5e3f0a0fb7d2e72fb9090f53753c330b.avif?t=1761467453\" width=200 height=200 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Welcome to Poodle Clicker, the most delightful clicker game you'll ever play! Dive into a world filled with adorable poodles of various colors and personalities, each bringing its own unique charm to your screen. Whether you're a casual gamer or a hardcore clicker enthusiast, Poodle Clicker has something for everyone!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Diverse Poodles:</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Discover poodles of all colors and personalities. From the warrior and wizard poodles to heavy metal poodles, goth poodles to the punk poodles, each one has a distinct look and attitude, making every click a joyful experience.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3077520/extras/d0a6b91dde3cf4be0da100a4b08cfbc7.avif?t=1761467453\" width=524 height=350 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>36 Original Songs:</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Enjoy a diverse soundtrack with 36 original songs that perfectly complement the vibe of the game. Each song adds to the fun and keeps you clicking along with the beat.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >(This game is full of metal songs!!)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Bonuses: </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >2x, 5x, Crit, +100, +250, +500 and AutoClick bonuses are the current bonuses will make you keep clicking!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3077520/extras/2092642593db4a5aaf99b553b9864057.avif?t=1761467453\" width=418 height=268 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Achievements and Leaderboards:</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Compete with friends and other players worldwide. Achieve milestones and climb the leaderboards to become the ultimate poodle clicker.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Kennel Upgrades:</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You can spend points to buy these upgrades. They will increase your click rate and automatically give you clicks as well!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Join the Fun:</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Step into the charming world of Poodle Clicker and start your clicking adventure today. Get ready to click and enjoy the cutest poodles on the planet!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Don't like AI?</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >If you don't like AI generated images or music, you can disable them in the main menu to replace them with real poodles and non AI generated music.</p>",
